videos.description: South Carolina gets out to a hot start, opening the game on a 9-0 run.
videos.headline: South Carolina starts the game on a 9-0 run

videos.description: Rakym Felder assist to Justin McKie for the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: South Carolina pads lead with wide-open 3-pointer

videos.description: Sindarius Thornwell gets the ball and drains the 3-pointer, his 4th of the half
videos.headline: South Carolina's Thornwell hits  fourth 3-pointer of the half

videos.description: Sindarius Thornwell fires a quick pass to Chris Silva who finishes with the dunk for South Carolina
videos.headline: Thornwell's quick assist leads to Silva's dunk

videos.description: Sindarius Thornwell steals the ball away from Auburn and passes to Justin McKie for the lay-in plus the foul.
videos.headline: Defense leads to offense for the Gamecocks

videos.description: Auburn's Austin Wiley misses both free throws, which earns everyone in attendance a free Chick-fil-A sandwich.
videos.headline: Auburn's misses at the line means free Chick-fil-A for everyone
